r />\n<br />\n呂小姐指出，涉事女警編號為 55827、26522。"},{"pid":"32c00efe4ceee9174e920fb0d67c1f64ca01b5d1","tid":1497823,"uid":271056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:56:44.000Z","msg":"死仆街黑狗乸!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d6cf51ba50ab601db62975bc98b5390a880119","tid":1497823,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6b4e79618ac2514cfb46c1167d2753d8fa5e3117","tid":1497823,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:55:56.000Z","msg":"【女示威者在警署被全裸 #凌辱】<br />\n<br />\n呂小姐：「被捕之後，是否無人權、失去對女性基本尊重？<br />\n<br />\n錯的不是我，為公義發聲是無錯。這件事之後我陷入抑鬱，害怕在街上見到警察。但當我聽到有  30 位手足在扣留中心被打到重傷，我決定要站出來發聲。」<br />\n<br />\n被捕示威者女小姐，出院後原定要上庭提堂，卻被帶去警署一間房間，被兩名女警要求脫去身上所有衣物，全裸「搜身」。呂小姐用手遮掩重要部位，更被女警用筆打手。呂小姐指，整個過程中其中一名女警用享受的眼神望著自己。<br />\n<br />\n完成全裸「搜身」過程打開房門，呂小姐發現有十幾個男警在門外等候。整個經歷，只能以「凌辱」形容。除了報復和發洩，還有甚麼解釋？<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n呂小姐指出，涉事女警編號為 55827、26522。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T06:57:01.000Z","msg":"報仇啦帬"},{"pid":"18acede9bbb05b2a0383773743ac9c79b6778559","tid":1497823,"uid":289681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"機場警區警署警長梁展鵬、警員郭志、趙國華及陳嘉、女警鍾麗媚、霍少清及麥穎兒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EpCwYPW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEpCwYPW.png&h=af996d85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4037a664d08735cc4ef7e51bdfb02e7cec025ae9","tid":1497823,"uid":180201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f0WReoR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%